==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-uːʃən|-uːʃən]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#''Business'' The act or process of explaining or proposing an approach to solving a [[problem]].
#''Chemistry'' A homogeneous mixture, which may be [[liquid]], [[gas]] or [[solid]], formed by disolving one or more substances.
#''Math'' The [[answer]] to a [[problem]].
#''Law'' Satisfaction of a claim or debt.

